Author: carrotlime
Text: That's literally my stats at my LW. 5'6" and 90 pounds. 14.5 BMI. eesh I'm gonna cry one sec

Author: IDontLikeLollipops
Text: Wtf is wrong with your coworkers tho. That's a bmi of 14.5. That's not like normal underweight-but-hot kind of thinking, that's lethal level.   Also I'm v sorry you're dealing with that. I had to deal with similar thinking for a while and it almost killed me. I hope you get okay.
